==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Neocomian
<hw>Ne`o*co"mi*an</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[From
<ets>Neocomium</ets>, the Latin name of Neuchatel, in Switzerland, where
these rocks occur.]</ety> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>A term applied to the
lowest deposits of the Cretaceous or chalk formation of Europe, being
the lower greensand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Neocomian</ent>⟦br⟧

