HEADWORD: Neocomian
<hw>Ne`o*co"mi*an</hw>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Geol.)</fld> <def>Of or
pertaining to the lower greensand.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

